Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:04.16,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,军人的脑子真是用石头做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:06.21,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:06.21,Default_Sub_Top,David,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:08.63,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,命运不也让我们连在一起了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:10.25,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,大家 地球就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:44.79,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,不 我们也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:48.17,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,亚瑟和西蒙尼也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:50.04,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,走吧 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.38,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,再见了 红色的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:59.58,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,为了活下去 为了回到地球 还有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:05.64,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,为了让大家知道地球迫在眉梢的危机 我们下定了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:11.15,Layzner_Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760)}空虚的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:24.99,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,全部好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.12,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.71,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,已经启动前往地球的轨道进程了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.71,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,亚瑟 大卫 可以从SPT里出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.00,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:37.34,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,要快点联络上友军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.00,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,快找出他们的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.30,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:41.85,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:45.62,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,真的能跟美军宇宙军舰队在这轨道上碰头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:47.22,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,应该可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:49.50,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,可是雷达上什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.70,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,对方有没有可能因为某种原因改变轨道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:53.81,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,不要乱作推测
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:57.50,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,友军轨道在R9104
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:59.86,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,确认好了 就快点跟他们联络
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:01.49,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:06.25,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,奇怪 这太空船也有人工重力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.83,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,喂 英二 情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.50,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,有什么我们可以帮得上忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.01,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,没 我一个人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:14.33,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,其他交给电脑就好了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.72,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,罗安 有你在就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.09,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,这里交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.76,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,有回应就通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:20.84,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.49,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,你要对他干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:24.60,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我只是要问他敌人的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:36.22,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我不知道你们怎么想的 但他是敌人 不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.26,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.75,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,成功脱离第四行星的重力圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.88,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,修正轨道往第三行星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:56.72,Default_Sub,Off2,0,0,0,,已确认在追踪中航天飞机的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:57.80,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,能赶上他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:02.31,Default_Sub,Off2,0,0,0,,等一下 有舰队极速接近该航天飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:03.37,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,有几艘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:04.52,Default_Sub,Off2,0,0,0,,三艘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:09.21,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,是古雷斯科说的地球舰队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:10.07,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,距离呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:11.94,Default_Sub,Off2,0,0,0,,2.02 方位不变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:15.90,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这样下去 在碰到航天飞机前会先跟该舰队遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:16.94,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.53,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,32±0.30
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.44,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.83,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,一遇到对方我们就先攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:24.71,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,准备第一波攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:30.63,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,前往地球的舰队的规模
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:32.71,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,还有他们拥有多少机动兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.34,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我是来告知地球的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.97,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不是来告诉你古拉多斯星的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.26,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,你只要回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.72,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,他不是间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.97,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我没有在问你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.15,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,知道美国宇宙军的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.15,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,出现在雷达上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:50.73,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.07,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,如少佐所说 在同一个轨道上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:56.26,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.74,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我想这样就能说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:03.74,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我是美国宇宙部队的运输舰阿斯洛托法克二号的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.54,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,卡克斯·丹尼少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:08.21,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我的识别编号是2010493
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.29,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:12.13,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我是美国宇宙军的丹尼少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:13.30,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:17.56,Default_Sub,Off1,0,0,0,,听得很清楚 这里是庞迪克 请说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.95,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我想直接跟舰长说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.18,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,有要紧的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.22,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.60,Default_Sub,Off1,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.14,Default_Sub,Off1,0,0,0,,我帮你转梅洛大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:26.43,Default_Sub,Off1,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.98,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我们会得救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:30.77,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,我是梅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:33.99,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,大佐 请快回收我们并改变航道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:39.21,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,你去好久了 你去火星怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:40.99,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,那里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:44.08,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,我不懂你在说什么 到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.91,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我军和苏联军的基地都被毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.83,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我亲眼看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.71,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,你说都毁了 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:54.88,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,因为外星人的介入 两个基地都被毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.34,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:01.93,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我知道很难相信 但真的有外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.93,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.05,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,敌人的机动兵器非常可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.94,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,大佐 如果你们去火星的话很鲁莽的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.81,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,少佐 难得你们联络上我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.40,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,不过我们不可能改变航路的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:19.83,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,我们的任务 是去调查失去联络的火星基地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:22.03,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,跟你们运输部队不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:25.99,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,大佐 相信我 外星人真的要来攻击我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:30.25,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,现在我跟地球的平民坐外星人的太空船逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:33.17,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,通信就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:39.06,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,我想你是不是被苏联军施以暴力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:40.90,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,你的意思是我是间谍吗 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:45.97,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,很可惜 我们没时间确认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:46.85,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,你不相信我是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.64,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,我会跟总部报告的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:50.81,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,大佐 拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:54.45,Default_Sub,Nero,0,0,0,,除了司令部的命令外我们是不能改变航道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:55.40,Default_Sub,Nero,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:56.61,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:57.49,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.78,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,他挂掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:03.86,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:07.95,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,跟你联络的是美军对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.70,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,为什么他们不相信你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.66,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我们会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:16.42,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,还没有敌人舰队的踪迹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:19.67,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,这样下去我们会跟美军错过的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:37.69,Default_Sub,Off1,0,0,0,,坐标243处确定有三艘敌人的巡洋战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:42.86,Default_Sub,Off1,0,0,0,,照原定轨道在08.20±0.05会进行遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.53,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,好 准备攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:46.62,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,准备我的黑色凯萨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.79,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,我也要出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:49.16,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.29,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,你要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:58.04,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,说不定可以发出信号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.80,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,帮我调成可以闪红灯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.63,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,约在4700处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:03.47,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:10.39,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,大佐 不明部队接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:11.43,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,把声音调大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:15.19,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,身份不明 要改变航道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:17.31,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,我也不知道怎么回事 先看着办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:18.94,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,是刚才的大佐的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:19.73,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:20.65,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,梅洛大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:21.69,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:22.57,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:23.69,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,是新兵器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.28,Default_Sub,Off2,0,0,0,,有五架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.24,Default_Sub,Off3,0,0,0,,大佐 刚才回报不是有说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:30.04,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,笨蛋 你是说那是外星人的机动兵器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.20,Default_Sub,Off2,0,0,0,,接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:33.20,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,以防万一 进入战斗位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.50,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,大佐 不要战斗 快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.51,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,救人啊 去救他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:44.38,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:48.22,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我们的太空船没回航的燃料了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:53.68,Default_Sub,Willow,0,0,0,,引擎被摧毁了 快射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.60,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,大佐 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.19,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,从雷达上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.11,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,三艘都
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:07.32,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,大家都被消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.37,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不快一点的话接下来就换我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:12.45,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.80,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,他们真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:23.39,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,如果他们相信我们的话 就不会增加无谓的牺牲者了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:25.71,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,他们跟我们不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:29.68,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,军人的脑子真是石头做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:34.16,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,刚才的战斗的信息 我军应该也接收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.36,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.60,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,马上就会跟来调查的部队碰头了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.77,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,如果没有的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.79,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,乖乖听我的就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.79,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,作战完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:57.74,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,去追航天飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:58.40,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:09:59.83,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:02.38,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,都没有地球的船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:03.54,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不要灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.42,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我们这边单独呼叫看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:06.67,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,说不定有人会收到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:07.67,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.88,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,雷达上什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:12.77,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.58,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,都活到现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.31,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,美国宇宙部队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:19.30,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.60,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,美国宇宙部队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.69,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:23.94,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我好累哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:24.94,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.90,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,美国宇宙部队请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.24,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,美国宇宙部队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:34.84,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,为什么只有我们要遭受这种待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:38.33,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,美国宇宙部队 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:45.10,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,雷达上有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:45.59,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:47.98,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,好像不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:51.34,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,这里是美国宇宙部队的丹尼少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.38,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:55.80,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我们目前的位置在24 38 26 14
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:56.78,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,请求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:58.06,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.27,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,请求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:01.85,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,为什么不回答我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:05.52,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,雷达显示的推测位置明明就非常近的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.38,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二 通信频道没搞错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.28,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.65,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,是苏联军舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.41,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,对了 一定是苏联军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.43,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,所以才没回我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:18.45,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,的确 这样的话是说得通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:21.79,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,不知道苏联军的通信频道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:24.79,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,试试各种频道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:28.17,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,苏联军也是来救援的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:30.58,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,因此才会到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:32.72,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,那就请继续联络
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.97,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,请继续联络他们请求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:36.76,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:40.00,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,这时候已经没有选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:41.39,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,换我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.19,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,不 我来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:46.45,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,这样下去苏联军会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:49.53,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,这里是美国宇宙部队丹尼少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:53.81,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,根据国际宇宙救助法请求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:57.66,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,接下来要不要听我的话 由贵舰自行决定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:02.33,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,再往火星去的话 对你们来说是非常危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:04.66,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,火星因为外星人的介入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:08.34,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,不只是我军 连你们的基地也被毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:12.07,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我们是坐外星人的太空船逃出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:16.93,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,刚才不听我警告的友军部队 已被外星人消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:19.65,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,真的有外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.77,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,现在我坐的船上有一名古拉多斯星人的俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.04,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我们要求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.48,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:39.74,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.50,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,你们一定有听到的 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.41,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,又是一样的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:45.87,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,军人都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:48.54,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,国际宇宙救助法是做什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:51.82,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,那不是以美苏为中心所订的国际法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.71,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,给我安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:58.59,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,再警告一次 请回头 快点改变航道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:03.01,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,外星人为了要征服地球 先镇压了火星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:05.43,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,详情等你们救了我们 我会详细说明的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:08.35,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,期待你们贵舰舰长英明的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:12.40,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,如那太空船报告中所说 有不明舰队接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:13.64,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:16.36,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,我也不知道怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.01,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.78,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,请回头 要不至少救救地球的平民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:25.37,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,这里是苏联太空部队第二舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.41,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,我们接受你们的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:30.50,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,接下来告诉你们停船的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:31.38,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:38.51,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,贵舰维持原来速度把航道改到3446-3548处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:41.68,Default_Sub,Off,0,0,0,,接下来再等候我们的引导通知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:42.35,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:44.47,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:46.18,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,得救了 安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.85,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,太好了 可以回地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.98,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,太好了 我们能回地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:52.63,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们能回地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:53.44,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.97,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,要把英二交给他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:01.03,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:03.52,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,军队就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.00,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,要让他变成苏联军的俘虏是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:07.48,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:10.46,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,为什么 他做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.21,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,把他当俘虏太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:14.46,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大家 不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:20.93,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我会来 就是为了通知地球迫近的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:24.07,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,只要能成功的话 当哪边的俘虏都行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:58.96,Default_Sub,Chefrengrev,0,0,0,,我是舰长基夫连科
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.51,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我是卡克斯·丹尼少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:03.30,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,感谢舰长英明的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:05.43,Default_Sub,Chef,0,0,0,,不 这是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:09.05,Default_Sub,Chef,0,0,0,,对了 你说外星人是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.06,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:11.94,Default_Sub,Chef,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:20.44,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,等一下 要把英二怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.40,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你们想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.15,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.15,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,不要去 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.74,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,请叫丹尼少佐来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.45,Default_Sub,Soldier,0,0,0,,他现在在跟舰长说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:27.03,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:27.83,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:28.62,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.55,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.80,Default_Sub,Chef,0,0,0,,你说的我大概了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.72,Default_Sub,Chef,0,0,0,,如果是真的话就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.34,Default_Sub,Chef,0,0,0,,谢谢你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.68,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,这是地球的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:52.02,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,请快把这事通知地球并尽快想出对策
